com.scalar.dl.ledger.crypto

Class CertificateEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.scalar.dl.ledger.crypto.CertificateEntry

  • @Immutable
public class CertificateEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    Container for a registered certificate and data about that certificate. In addition to the certificate, a CertificateEntry will keep track of:
    • the certificate holder id
    • the certificate version
    • the time in which the certificate was registered
